#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_reference.rst:16
msgid "Base class for reference-counted objects."
msgstr "引用计数对象的基类。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_reference.rst:19
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_reference.rst:21
msgid ""
"Base class for any object that keeps a reference count. :ref:`Resource "
"<class_Resource>` and many other helper objects inherit this class."
msgstr "保留引用计数的任何对象的基类。:ref:`Resource <class_Resource>` 和其他许多帮助类都继承了此类。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_reference.rst:23
msgid ""
"References keep an internal reference counter so that they are "
"automatically released when no longer in use, and only then. References "
"therefore do not need to be freed manually with :ref:`Object.free "
"<class_Object_method_free>`."
msgstr ""
"引用保留一个内部引用计数器，以便它们在且仅在不再使用时自动释放。因此，引用不需要使用 :ref:`Object.free "
"<class_Object_method_free>` 手动释放。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_reference.rst:25
msgid ""
"In the vast majority of use cases, instantiating and using "
"``Reference``-derived types is all you need to do. The methods provided "
"in this class are only for advanced users, and can cause issues if "
"misused."
msgstr ""
"在绝大多数用例中，实例化和使用 ``Reference`` "
"派生的类型，就是您要做的一切。此类中提供的方法仅适用于高级用户，如果使用不当，可能会引起问题。"

